data.title: Hiram R. Burton
data.meta_description: Hiram Rodney Burton was an American physician and politician from Lewes, in Sussex County, Delaware. A member of the Republican Party, Burton served two terms as Delaware's at-large U.S. Representative from 1905 to 1909.
